ALDI is bringing 50 new jobs to Cambuslang with the opening of its latest supermarket. Aldi delivers jobs bonus at new store ALDI is bringing 50 new jobs to Cambuslang with the opening of its latest supermarket.Bosses said roles are still up for grabs at the new store, with positions available to view on www.aldirecruitment.co.ukTo mark the opening of the School Avenue outlet, the shop is giving away golden tickets to win prizes, including TVs and smart phones.The shop opens on Thursday, at 8am. 